				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/Chung-Nam-bi%E1%BB%87t-nghi%E1%BB%87p/poem-aojK5yt7X8rTWmkDYWXgEg">Chung Nam biệt nghiệp - 終南別業</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Duy/author-9f1Hth0gmM_PXzGNXg5Fog">Vương Duy</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-Ph%C3%B9-Phong-ch%E1%BB%A7-nh%C3%A2n-%C4%91%C3%A1p/poem-JIfVl-3ILF4CeMtEfeNxgA">Đại Phù Phong chủ nhân đáp - 代扶風主人答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-X%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Linh/author-Q_JpPOHTIyzNkB76eQk-WQ">Vương Xương Linh</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-Trung-Ch%C3%A2u-Long-H%C6%B0ng-t%E1%BB%B1-s%E1%BB%9F-c%C6%B0-vi%E1%BB%87n-b%C3%ADch/poem-D8MxhG9NzDMD7H9xTpErMQ">Đề Trung Châu Long Hưng tự sở cư viện bích - 題忠州龍興寺所居院壁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Chi%E1%BA%BFu-L%C3%A2n/H%C3%A0-xuy%C3%AAn-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-phi%E1%BA%BFm/poem-ME97xe2si2d-mcSUujXCrA">Hà xuyên độc phiếm - 葭川獨泛</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0-Chi%E1%BA%BFu-L%C3%A2n/author-WXzhH3pS40_UOcZwZtHC5A">Lư Chiếu Lân</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Dung/H%C3%A0n-th%E1%BB%B1c-d%E1%BA%A1/poem-49mQY2XjO0ty1TgffIdKXQ">Hàn thực dạ - 寒食夜</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%B4i-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Dung/author-wMO6FIOpo5WKstlu9gI9Ww">Thôi Đạo Dung</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-h%C3%A0n-l%C3%A2m-Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BB%A9-h%E1%BB%8Dc-s%C4%A9/poem--E9BDvBT_Tl3sH5Hs2tTbA">Tặng hàn lâm Trương tứ học sĩ - 贈翰林張四學士</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="h